{"tid":11480,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好似我咁痴線","createTime":"2016-11-29T10:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T09:36:06.000Z","uid":33359,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb084af45218a8a3a6703160f5fb3e65a72d59e","tid":11480,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"話說大約兩年前 未搵到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到九展間星影匯請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就sd cv過去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁無回音 可能請到人啦 咁我無理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔幾日又見佢出post請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我又sd 點知又係無回音 但係隔幾日佢又出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是我就嬲嬲地 每隔幾日就sd封cv 過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又驚佢block 我email 所以就轉幾個email咁sd過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如是者 咁就sd 左兩年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家既我一早搵到穩定工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係收工之後無野做都會sd封過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我要等到佢約我見工 之後比我拒絕既一日黎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7054831f2656ba1f8ffa65b68f6ca9ff86e4408","tid":11480,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52b2e120b422fedf170580613cf8e8157e49e06","tid":11480,"uid":39484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:11:13.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dfd0701c0303781881fe05ed91c6c3d9729aa